            "description": "Even master adventurers need proper rest! Linnea summons Lumi to strike in <color=#FFD780FF>{LINK#N11300001}Super Power Form{/LINK}</color>, healing nearby party members. For a short duration, she will continuously heal nearby active party members based on Linnea's DEF.\\nIf Lumi has already struck when unleashing Elemental Burst, Lumi's active duration will be reset instead. Lumi's Strike Form will not change."
